.DS_Store

# Generated documentation artefacts. Rebuilt by `npm run build:docs`
# (the auto-patch / release pipeline regenerates them on every
# version bump). The SVGs are kept in git because they are the
# images embedded in README.md (Excalifont is inlined so they
# render with the hand-drawn look in the GitHub README) — without
# them GitHub's rendered README would show broken thumbnails. The
# PNGs are kept too as a fallback for renderers that don't allow
# SVG.
docs/ressources/generated/puml/
docs/ressources/generated/excalidraw/
